   * 0 seconds && < 60 seconds        Now
   * 60 seconds                       1 Minute
   * > 60 seconds && < 60 minutes     X Minutes
   * 60 minutes                       1 Hour
   * > 60 minutes && < 24 hours       X Hours
   * 24 hours                         1 Day
   * > 24 hours && < 7 days           X Days
   * 7 days                           1 Week
   * > 7 days && < ~ 1 Month          X Weeks
   * ~ 1 Month                        1 Month
   * > ~ 1 Month && < 1 Year          X Months
   * 1 Year                           1 Year
   * > 1 Year                         X Years
